features: A Must for an Organized Office: It’s easy to keep your documents organized and always at hand with the Darice plastic folders with pockets and prongs! Secure and versatile, these pocket folders with prongs help you organize your files and reduce clutter while bringing a colorful touch to the office decor!

Easy Document Organization: Featuring two 4 ½-inches high pockets, one on each side, 3 prongs and a business card slot, our 2-pocket folder allows you to store and organize your documents more efficiently, keeping them safe and ensuring quick access.

Durable and Resistant: These 3 prong folders with pockets are made with durable plastic, which is thick yet flexible and durable. The folders are also waterproof, tear-resistant and very easy to clean!
Convenient 24-Pcs Assorted Color Set: The school folders with pockets come in a convenient set of 24 pieces in 6 different colors, perfect for color-coding your documents and effortless organization!

Wide Range of Uses: Versatile, secure and reliable, our two pocket folders can be used at home, office, school, university, college, business, teaching, kindergarten or public institutions for storing important documents and organizing them with ease!
body.description: Plastic Folders with Pockets and Prongs for Optimal Document Organization and Storage Our 2-pocket folders are a simple and efficient solution to organize and store your documents more efficiently. These letter-size plastic folders have 4 ½-inch pockets, a business card slot and a 3-prong design, that allow you to store everything from important documents, homework, projects or brochures to business cards and other files. Made with durable plastic, these pocket folders are waterproof, tear-resistant and very durable, which means that your important documents and files are in safe hands. Still not convinced? Here are some of the amazing features of our plastic folders with pockets: 1. 24-pack plastic folders; 2. File folders with 2 pockets (4 ½-inch); 3. Business card slot; 4. 3-prong design; 5. Easy and efficient document organization; 6. Heavy-duty plastic; 7. Waterproof and tear-resistant; 8. Ideal letter size dimensions; 9. 6 colors per pack; 10. Suitable for a wide range of documents, files, brochures, drawings, projects; 11. Ideal for home, office, school, college; Stay organized and keep your documents safe with our plastic folders with pockets!

reviews.reviewText: The inside 3-prong piece gets caught on the inside pocket literally 50% of the timeI open it up, so I have to shove my hand in the middle as I close each thing. This is with or without paper inside unfortunately and it seems to be completely random.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for Organizing
reviews.reviewText: I had a big 2 year project to organize for college and these folders were perfect! The plastic is a nice durable thickness. 6 bright and bold colors, with 4 of each, perfect for color coding. The pockets hold multiple papers and the prongs hold a decent thickness of papers as well. I was pleasantly surprised by the wavy design set into the covers (matte vs shiny) as those didn’t show up in the pictures that I saw when I ordered the product. Definitely recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is a nice little set of folders. Since I use these folders for a variety of school related activities, the plastic folders hold up to the wear and tear as compared to paper. I really like the pins in the center as well as the pockets. Very well made and sturdy for daily use.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Colors and durability is great.
reviews.reviewText: These cost just under a dollar for each folder. That is the average price right now for plastic folders. I use these for my classroom. The 'business card' holder is used for login information. I have younger students. The paper folder option never works out unless they are replaced every semester. These plastic folders will last the entire school year or more. The colors are nice and vibrant.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for our daughter's school needs!
reviews.reviewText: Every year our daughter needs these plastic 2-pocket folders for pretty much all of her classes. This pack works out to be a little less than a dollar per folder and as they have prongs, it's not too bad of a price. They have a fun subtle swirl design, as well. We will see how they hold up, but they seem to be as sturdy as most other comparable folders I have seen out there. The colors are nice and bright and I like that there are so many different options since her classes typically need their own distinct folder color.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars I like them.
reviews.reviewText: This 24-Pack of Darice 2-Pocket Plastic Folders is very good to have. I really need folders like these to keep a lot of my papers organized! Medical records slipped right into the pockets and of course with all my genealogical research, I have copious amounts of papers that need to be sorted and these folders are perfect for that. They also have prongs to use on hole punched pages.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: We ordered these for my son’s school, the kids are always in need of additional folders to store their work. Durable, bright colors and hold up nicely.
